Package org.eclipse.core.databinding.bind.steps

Class ValueOneWaySteps

java.lang.Object
org.eclipse.core.databinding.bind.steps.ValueOneWaySteps
public final class ValueOneWaySteps extends Object
Contains Step interfaces for the fluent databinding API for one-way IObservableValue bindings. Each of these interfaces define the operations that are allowed in a particular pipeline step.
Since:
1.11
